'''DYDI-TV''' is a commercial television relay station in the [[Philippines]] owned by [[ABS-CBN Broadcasting Corporation]]. Its studio is located at [[Calbayog City]], [[Samar]].
==ABS-CBN TV-10 Program== *[[TV Patrol Tacloban]] (simulcast over TV-2 Tacloban and TV-7 Catbalogan)
